There are 4 test collections one for each category that could be run independently.
Each test collection is in the separate JSON file.
You will need Postman to run test collection.
Please, follow the next steps:
1. Download all files from the repository
2. Open Postman
3. Set up the environment:
 - Open "Manage environment" in the right upper corner.
 - Click "Import" and choose the file with the environment "localhost_Playground.postman_environment".
 - After downloading chose the environment from the environment dropdown (in the right upper corner).
 - Import collection JSON file "Import" button in the left upper corner.
 - Run the collection.